snippet.title: Super Mario Bros.: The Cookie of Destiny Luigi Gameplay
snippet.description:
Just showcasing some new stuff I've done in Cookie of Destiny. To name them:

- P-switches
- Coins
- Luigi Fully Playable
- Character Select Screen
- Finished Stage 1

go to http://forums.mfgg.net/viewtopic.php?f=8&t=12394 for more info on the project!
